title: Wiring and Lighting by Chris Kitcher
description:
Wiring and Lighting by Chris Kitcher

2013 | ISBN: 1847974163 | eISBN: 9781847975898 | English | 160 pages | EPUB | 17 MB

Wiring and Lighting provides a comprehensive guide to DIY wiring around the home. It sets out the regulations and legal requirements surrounding electrical installation work, giving clear guidelines that will enable the reader to understand what electrical work they are able to carry out, and what the testing and certification requirements are once the work is completed
